      <h1>Shopify Shipping Margin Calculator</h1>
      <p class="intro">Free shipping is the single biggest cause of invisible margin erosion for Shopify stores. This calculator finds your true break-even shipping threshold — so you're not giving profit away.</p>

      <section class="card">
        <p class="card-title">Enter your details</p>
        <form id="calcForm" novalidate>
          <div class="field"><label for="averageOrderValue">Average order value (£/$/€)</label><input type="number" id="averageOrderValue" name="averageOrderValue" placeholder="e.g. 45" min="0" required></div>
