<details>
  <summary>How do I calculate the right free shipping threshold for Shopify?</summary>
  <div class="faq-answer">Divide your average shipping cost + COGS by your target gross margin percentage. For most stores, the free shipping threshold should be set at 2–2.5x the average product cost to remain profitable after all fees.</div>
</details>
